Hi there.
"Full Europe", Does that mean it includes east i.e. Russian regions? I'm asking because I already have 2013.30 which doesn't include it... so is it a modified version?

Russian map is a separated release from Europe.

The latest release is City Navigator Russia NT 2013.30 Navicom (cyrillic language) but it isn't uploaded in TPB yet.
